      "side": 1,
      "message": "Thank you for this feedback. Updated: the design is now \"Sub-Device State Management\" with a shared common layer and per-type binaries following the dbus-sensors pattern. NIC, PCIe card, or any other sub-device type is additive: new PDI interface, new binary on top of the shared layer, no changes to existing types. Drive is the first consumer.",
