      "side": 1,
      "message": "How do you handle the relationship between the overall system and the sub-device (ie. drive)?  When the host is _off_ you also want the state of the drive to be represented as _off_.  When the host is _off_, you probably want the drive to give an error if someone asks for it to be _on_.  I don\u0027t see any words to talk about this relationship.",
